Lucy – Captured stunning, detailed images of asteroid Donaldjohanson during a fly‑by on April 20 2025 as the spacecraft heads toward the distant Trojan asteroids.  

3D Tissue Chips – Developing tissue chips that can be used for modeling of acute and/or chronic exposures for 6 months or longer.  
